'''line_reverse_mode''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets conditions where trains can reverse direction.<br><br>
0 = at end of line, and at stations<br>
1 = at end of line only<br>

<pre>
[difficulty]
line_reverse_mode = 0
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 ]

'''Default:''' 0


